        {
            "title": "AI太強反成威脅？鮑爾與貝森特會銀行巨頭 聚焦Anthropic新模型資安風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bOtWAQ7rvmBIJ6hAiNCD2A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/d4d59484fb843d974b6e63fc5389719b\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/ai%E5%A4%AA%E5%BC%B7%E5%8F%8D%E6%88%90%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85-%E9%AE%91%E7%88%BE%E8%88%87%E8%B2%9D%E6%A3%AE%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%83%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD-%E8%81%9A%E7%84%A6anthropic%E6%96%B0%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E8%B3%87%E5%AE%89%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-190002322.html",
